ISLAMABAD, Jul 05 (APP): The Ministry of Interior on Friday clarified that it had not taken any decision regarding the closure of Internet services during Muharram-ul-Haram.
A ministry spokesperson, in a statement, said requests had been received from the provinces in that regard, but the ministry had yet taken any decision on them.
